# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:346
msgid ""
"These guidelines are designed to maximize the interoperability of submitted "
"national data by clearly defining its conditions of reuse. Interoperability "
"and synergies in information exchange between Conventions is only possible "
"when data can be legally, confidently, and consistently reused across "
"systems, which requires reuse conditions that are both explicit and "
"standardized."
msgstr ""
"Estas directrices están diseñadas para maximizar la interoperabilidad de los"
" datos nacionales presentados definiendo claramente sus condiciones de "
"reutilización. La interoperabilidad y las sinergias en el intercambio de "
"información entre Convenios sólo son posibles cuando los datos pueden "
"reutilizarse de forma legal, segura y coherente en todos los sistemas, lo "
"que requiere unas condiciones de reutilización que sean explícitas y estén "
"normalizadas."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:348
msgid ""
"You can read more about the licences in Annex I of these guidelines and you "
