#: ../../introduction.md:391
msgid "Recalculations and time series consistency"
msgstr "Repetir los cálculos y la consistencia de las series cronológicas"

#: ../../introduction.md:393
msgid ""
"Advances in methodologies and data availability may require periodic "
"recalculations of previously submitted national estimates. While "
"recalculations may require refinements in terms of target-setting, they "
"ensure the consistency of the time series and the comparability between the "
"baseline and future monitoring data."
msgstr ""
"Los avances en materia de metodologías y disponibilidad de los datos pueden "
"requerir que, cada cierto tiempo, vuelvan a calcularse las estimaciones "
"nacionales remitidas previamente. Si bien dichos cálculos pueden necesitar "
"reajustes en cuanto a las metas establecidas, garantizan la consistencia de "
"las series cronológicas y la comparabilidad entre los datos de referencia y "
"los futuros datos de seguimiento."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:396
msgid ""
"For instance, given the evolution of the calculation methods presented in "
"version 2 of the [Good Practice Guidance for SDG Indicator "
"15.3.1](https://www.unccd.int/publications/good-practice-guidance-sdg-"
"indicator-1531-proportion-land-degraded-over-total-land) and its "
"[Addendum](https://www.unccd.int/resources/manuals-and-guides/addendum-good-"
"practice-guidance-sdg-indicator-1531-proportion-land), it is recommended "
"that previously submitted estimates of all SO1 indicators, including SDG "
"Indicator 15.3.1, be recalculated and included in the national report to be "
"submitted in 2026. Default national estimates provided through the PRAIS "
"forms have already been recalculated for country Parties using the new "
"calculation methods."
msgstr ""
"Por ejemplo, dada la evolución de los métodos de cálculo presentados en la "
"versión 2 de la [Guía de buenas prácticas para el indicador 15.3.1 de los "
"ODS](https://www.unccd.int/publications/good-practice-guidance-sdg-"
"indicator-1531-proportion-land-degraded-over-total-land) y su "
"[Adenda](https://www.unccd.int/resources/manuals-and-guides/addendum-good-"
"practice-guidance-sdg-indicator-1531-proportion-land), se recomienda que las"
" estimaciones presentadas anteriormente de todos los indicadores del OE1, "
"incluido el indicador 15.3.1 de los ODS, se vuelvan a calcular y se incluyan"
" en el informe nacional que se presentará en 2026. Las estimaciones "
"nacionales por defecto proporcionadas a través de los formularios PRAIS ya "
"han sido recalculadas para los países Partes utilizando los nuevos métodos "
"de cálculo."

#: ../../introduction.md:399
msgid ""
"For a broader discussion on the issue of recalculations, see chapter 6 of "
"version 2 of the [Good Practice Guidance for SDG Indicator "
"15.3.1](https://www.unccd.int/publications/good-practice-guidance-sdg-"
"indicator-1531-proportion-land-degraded-over-total-land)."
msgstr ""
